{"tid":2211583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE子瑜為什麼能稱「女團真人美貌第一人」！看看路人鏡頭下的她有多美","createTime":"2020-09-21T08:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T12:09:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":23,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"04826f246a5ab52272598e323e4f8f0a62d2df28","tid":2211583,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"女團TWICE老幺子瑜，她的美貌被認為完美得無話可說，不僅男生喜歡她，就連女生也覺得她可愛。<br />\n<br />\n雜誌寫真照和官方活動圖有精修的嫌疑，最能展現真顏值的自然要數街拍照了。 路人鏡頭下的子瑜的顏值確實很高，而且還不是一般的高。<br />\n<br />\n子瑜小巧的面龐和其白皙透亮的肌膚，加上凹凸有致的好身材，即使在一群人之間也屬她最亮眼。<br />\n<br />\n套用塵世間的形容詞，這就是「仙氣」~<br />\n<br />\n據目擊過子瑜真人的路人表示她臉小腿長身材纖細，自帶明星光環，在路上遠遠地看見就會讓人產生「那個人肯定是藝人」的感覺，並且真人比照片還要美！不愧是女團真人美貌第一人！顏值、身高、身材全都擁有，難怪被粉絲們調侃「太自私了」。"},{"pid":"5b5c4db1a3df926b62425d0bf6a369407e90cc88","tid":2211583,"uid":16659,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d5d8e47186ee6049446a4fba3b054d57/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130165-874181.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d5d8e47186ee6049446a4fba3b054d57%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130165-874181.jpeg&h=3e9dc551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f361057d4604ac3b99f449b4709d3608/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130165-874189.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f361057d4604ac3b99f449b4709d3608%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130165-874189.jpeg&h=43399a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_070e10d6b29bd2fd505271f0efaff034/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130165-874186.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_070e10d6b29bd2fd505271f0efaff034%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130165-874186.jpeg&h=21bd3b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s